flowRoot.flowPara: Joseph Weizenbaum, inventor of ELIZA, Developer of First US Air Deffence System, Humanist, ... found one of the best language hacks i ever heard: "Krieg ist der Feind" (german: War is the Enemy). I extended it so that younger people also understand what i think he meant. "Not USA is the enemy, not russia is the enemy, not ost timor is the enemy, the act fighting against each other is the enemy" there are good and bad people in all coutries, religions, skin colors, companies...
i bought "Rebel at Work" and "Krieg ist der Feind" from Joseph Weizenbaum and i'm satisfied with this two products.
